thread.title: Jacinta
thread.title_full: The Vet Shed reviewed by Jacinta

author: Jacinta
title: Jacinta
text: After having some trouble using AfterPay, I called the phone number supplied for The Vet Shed. The Customer Service I received was quick and resolved my issue exactly. I still has some trouble so I emailed and their response again was incredibly quick and had already resolved the issue again. (Issues were no fault of the Vet Shed). Order was dispatched same day and arrived only a couple of days later! Incredibly Impressed and have recommended to my family.
